    "Named-entity recognition taskIn this section, we show the results of different models on named-entity recognition task and show the explanation.",
    "ResultsThe results of the NER task are shown in Table 9.",
    "Discussion of named-entity recognition resultThe first reason why the ALBERT model performs well is the use of Sentence Oder Prediction (SOP) in the pre-training phase.",
    "Compared with the NSP used in the BERT model, SOP performs better in downstream tasks.",
